description:
First Berserker Khazan Review - BRUTAL, Polished and Absolutely ADDICTIVE
In this The First Berserker: Khazan Review, we’ll take an in-depth look at the first-ever Singleplayer ARPG set in the Dungeon & Fighter universe, developed by Neople and published by Nexon, and decide whether this team’s first souls-like has delivered on the expectations it generated from its highly praised demo that came out earlier this year. Read on to find out!
